reviewText: this dvd is a must for anyone who is looking to succeed in the music business. so much great information that has a lasting impact on the serious person who wants to make it in this tough music industry. Schofield is superb!!!

This film is priceless, a must have for all who aspire to make it into the music industry. The step by step guidance given by major labels executives is invaluable. Following the steps given in this film will allow anyone who seek stardom to obtain it.
